## 🔹 11. Common Mistake ❌

👉 Directly putting:

* if-else (roles)
* logging
* caching

inside main class ❌

👉 Always move to Proxy ✅

---

## 🔹 12. Important Interview Insight

👉 Proxy **never comes alone**

Usually used with:

* Strategy Pattern
* Builder Pattern
* Command Pattern

---

## 🔹 13. Final Recap 🚀

* Separate extra responsibilities
* Create Proxy class
* Proxy holds real object
* Client uses Proxy (NOT real class)

